This one is pretty good. :3
R/S/E had some pretty catchy music... The thing that was sad about this gen (for me) was that they stopped naming the towns and cities after colors...
My favorite songs from this game are the songs for route 113 (ash falling) and route 111 (desert).
Those are my favorite routes, too... along with the ones on both sides of Fortree. ^-^
